    <h1>Real-Time Bidding (RTB)</h1>
    <p class="description">The programmatic process of buying and selling <strong>individual ad impressions</strong> through automated auctions that complete in under 100 milliseconds — each bid priced on the specific user's value to that advertiser at that moment.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
